  <brief_title>Laparoscopic Internal Gastric Banding, New Simple and Costless Weight Loss Procedure</brief_title>
  <acronym>LIGB</acronym>
  <official_title>Study the Effectiveness and Safety of Laparoscopic Internal Gastric Banding, New Simple and Costless Weight Loss Procedure, in Comparison to Laparoscopic Sleeve Gastrectomy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
